    "monster1034": "<h1 class=monster>The Seer<br><span class=type>Medium natural humanoid human , human</span><br><span class=level>Level 4 Brute<span class=xp> XP 175</span></span> </h1> <p class=flavor><b>Initiative</b> +3        <b>Senses</b> Perception +2<br><b>HP</b> 66; <b>Bloodied</b> 33<br><b>AC</b> 15; <b>Fortitude</b> 15, <b>Reflex</b> 14, <b>Will</b> 14<br><b>Speed</b> 6</p><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Chain</b> (standard, at-will) ✦ <b>Weapon</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>+7 vs AC; 1d6+4 damage. </p><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Summoning Scream</b></p><p class=flavorIndent>The Seer summons allies as described under Setup.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Alignment</b> Evil       <b> Languages</b> Common<br><b>Skills</b> Athletics +10, Endurance +10<br><b>Str</b> 17 (+5)      <b>Dex</b> 12 (+3)      <b>Wis</b> 11 (+2)<br><b>Con</b> 16 (+5)      <b>Int</b> 10 (+2)      <b>Cha</b> 12 (+3)</p><br><p class=publishedIn>Published in Dungeon Magazine 155, page(s) 87.</p>",
